'''Tacirra''' d aẓru yesɛan timeẓri n tifarkitin dɣa yetwegzem s tafilin tirqaqin neɣ « tifarkitin n uẓru ». Yezmer ad yili d-aẓru n talaɣt, neɣ yezmer ad yilli d-aẓru yetbeddelen timeẓri-s ddaw aẓɣal neɣ adad.

Deg timiḍi wis 15 di tmurt n [[Ṭṭalyan]], Cirra n talaɣt, yetsseqdec am ufanim yetaken ajeṛṛiḍ s ini yetṛuḥun seg aberkan ar udemdam i ussuneɣ n ilsanen.


